{"tid":2347544,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地有冇玩過d 咩小遊戲好難忘？","createTime":"2020-12-31T06:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T09:21:16.000Z","uid":104580,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dc422019ad78cfeca70768c6e02aa4b2aedf5ce4","tid":2347544,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:36:54.000Z","msg":"最近出左隻交友app 開始多人玩<br />\n見到好多user好鐘意入面兩隻小遊戲(猜猜畫畫同契合度測試)，但我知大家好快會玩悶<br />\n所以依家想研究多d小遊戲，有冇人可以拋低d 小遊戲或者兒時回憶<br />\n<br />\n我暫時諗到第三個遊戲係 估歌仔？<br />\n我可以搵d姐姐去幫手唱返一百幾十首廣東話(副歌)歌再俾大家估<br />\n應該好容易幫大家打開到話題"},{"pid":"85186da2f178d7b86ba3c3e947eec4a7822a11d8","tid":2347544,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"Wt app"},{"pid":"8ef332f90a2b4ff4010153b797d089f2d46b2e37","tid":2347544,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"長玩啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"29e4d0d64af89a80b68561e6bfee06fcfc5baf51","tid":2347544,"uid":314731,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:40:02.000Z","msg":"DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a11123e5ab0cf70fb42448d7c1e6087a972dfe","tid":2347544,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"想借位搵隻小遊戲<br />\n細個果陣玩過 可以打電腦/雙打對戰<br />\n玩家要係咁禁個Keyboard嘅兩個制去生啲生物出嚟去打交<br />\n好似一邊係黑色一邊係白色<br />\n之後黑同白色就會打交 總之打完之後場上面仲有生物果邊就贏<br />\n冇記錯嘅話一隻生物殺完人自己都會死 所以要贏嘅話一定要生多過對面2者以上 有冇師兄知係咩Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374f5e72145cf83287cbd8d16016556cdef75d1d","tid":2347544,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29e4d0d64af89a80b68561e6bfee06fcfc5baf51","tid":2347544,"uid":314731,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:40:02.000Z","msg":"DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個英文版的追求女仔遊戲，考驗你能否在一